{"tid":1983163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國官員：政府已確定容許華為參與5G建設","createTime":"2020-04-21T15:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T09:24:18.000Z","uid":2054,"like":18,"dislike":144,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"063df5ed51c0c4ae859452b2900ee0ce4b13058f","tid":1983163,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1282432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1282432&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=1f9d60cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1282432</a><br />\n<br />\n英國官員：政府已確定容許華為參與5G建設<br />\n21.04.2020 23:24<br />\n英國政府高層官員透露，英國政府已確定，容許中國電訊設備製造商華為，在英國建設5G電訊網絡中存有角色，但否認英國政府是改變決定。英國外交部常務次官麥克唐納向國會議員表示，政府決定容許華為繼續投資當地5G市場，但會有嚴格條件，又認為做法並非對華為重開市場，強調中國是英國非常重要的合作夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府在一月決定，容許華為參與非敏感部份的5G網絡建設，市場份額最多三成半。"},{"pid":"b82f707442ee52390646f88eb52bc1600042d94d","tid":1983163,"uid":21545,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:36:46.000Z","msg":"天黑廢國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be64b6fd502c60e1a82efd3706d42bb72b5d140","tid":1983163,"uid":104138,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"九成中國比左好多甜頭日落國啦"},{"pid":"80ca23a6ec3b1bca5233c7ee84d713c2e2efaba4","tid":1983163,"uid":126782,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"仲覺得英國會幫香港啲連登仔去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地首相都中埋武肺 都要繼續奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04dca81f1c566574bd8c92f0c28d6cb4c15601e","tid